Installing BANDIT on the HOST system
====================================

Install a copy of BANDIT into the HOST /opt directory.
# cd /opt
# tar -xvf bandit-1.3.tar.xz 
# cd bandit-1.3 

Initialize the HOST environment for BANDIT from the bandit home directory:
# source bin/bandit-set

Bandit should work now in the HOST. Test with:
# bandit --version

Read the file RAISE to learn how to use the BANDIT to raise a new TARGET system.

